{"tid":1631879,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【factcheck正視聽】聯合國人權大佬講嘢，你要聽","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:29:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T19:24:38.000Z","uid":138409,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"8abaa071cd707ceda66904a23b569b6e08e5d234","tid":1631879,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:29:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1630790/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1630790/page/1</a><br />\n之前UN人權大佬Michelle Bachelet話香港示威越黎越暴力令佢感到「困擾」<br />\n隔離post成班人即刻上曬腦<br />\n響度屌話「人權理事會」無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />意見無參考價值<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">tl;dr<br />\n佢唔係黎自垃圾嘅人權理事會<br />\n佢唔係黎自垃圾嘅人權理事會<br />\n佢唔係黎自垃圾嘅人權理事會<br />\n<br />\n佢係有返咁上下份量<br />\n佢嘅意見值得我地參考同警惕</span><br />\n----------------------------------------------<br />\nFactcheck先<br />\nMichelle Bachelet唔係黎自人權理事會<br />\n佢係high commissioner (人權事務高級專員)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ohchr.org/en/aboutus/pages/highcommissioner.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ohchr.org%2Fen%2Faboutus%2Fpages%2Fhighcommissioner.aspx&d=lN%2BDZ8lYvPdYiEl1IYcsL2dKmUD4oZ9Yq66eb74BBG8%3D&h=683a8601\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ohchr.org/en/aboutus/pages/highcommissioner.aspx</a><br />\nOn September 1, 2018 Michelle Bachelet assumed her functions as the United Nations High Commissioner for Human Rights<br />\n<br />\nOHCHR（人權事務高級專員辦公室）同埋UNHRC（人權理事會）<span style=\"color: gold;\">兩樣嘢係獨立㗎</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.ohchr.org/english/press/hrc/kit/hrcs_fs2.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.ohchr.org%2Fenglish%2Fpress%2Fhrc%2Fkit%2Fhrcs_fs2.pdf&d=lN%2BDZ8lYvPdYiEl1IYcsL2dKmUD4oZ9Yq66eb74BBG8%3D&h=8f34782b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.ohchr.org/english/press/hrc/kit/hrcs_fs2.pdf</a><br />\nThe Human Rights Council, consisting of State representatives and reporting directly to the General Assembly, is a political body with a comprehensive human rights mandate and <span style=\"color: gold;\">a distinct entity from OHCHR</span><br />\n<br />\n問過法夢比卡超嘅意見<br />\n<br />\n用一個唔係完全準確的比喻，high commissioner係聯合國人權事務方面的行政機關首長<br />\n所有負責接收投訴、進行調查等等的工作全部係OHCHR做<br />\n當然high commisioner本身都係國際關係中有地位的人<br />\n好多時係小國的前外交官或總統<br />\n以盡量確保獨立性<br />\n<br />\n至於人權理事會 UNHRC，算係立法機關，大家都知成員好多都係本身唔尊重人權的國家<br />\n要採取行動就要投票<br />\n如果投票通過了某個resolution<br />\n可以話係國家之間的consensus咁囉<br />\n都係道德壓力咁解，無實際約束力<br />\n<br />\n佢哋亦都可以決議譬如話要委任一個special rapporteur調查某國家人權問題咁<br />\nspecial rapporteur多數係學者/法官<br />\n然後真係落手落腳做的就是OHCHR<br />\n<br />\n所以high commissioner主要負責行政、物流方面嘅support，佢亦都會每年寫人權報告<br />\n不過通常都係重複返special rapporteur 或者 人權條約機構 講過嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n即係好似UN 本身咁<br />\n係人都知安理會最大<span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n但係你唔會話秘書長係廢㗎嘛<br />\n淨係個symbolic meaning都不得了啦</span>"},{"pid":"42dba3f7aedc62cfbf97ce054d828865984d4d17","tid":1631879,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:31:01.000Z","msg":"我正式宣布！聽日係全民文宣日！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631729\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631729</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6ec4726cb35abaad2c462aa1c4c7f5e27ca46272","tid":1631879,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:31:29.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"f9c299566e59b3f9e453f5cbbc62a6f31e959f0c","tid":1631879,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:31:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1c59b5fb4348d813a888e5a142fe6d54d62c5566","tid":1631879,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:31:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d97228fb4d717b2365b59589f4c8e2b89b07f8f1","tid":1631879,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:32:16.000Z","msg":"民意已逆轉"},{"pid":"2fa6ae4a962146593ba0fb5fc639ef9d520aa4b0","tid":1631879,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:33:56.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7f917fe2741ccbc12637e00972329832b917ea24","tid":1631879,"uid":288707,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:35:34.000Z","msg":"請各位記得當初用#StandwithHK既時候,就係想國際社會幫我地<br />\n現在盡量唔好做一D事令佢地離開<br />\n港共係外國落廣告已經證明左佢地好關心外國勢力<br />\n對民意係WFC, 唔好俾港共成功"},{"pid":"86ea38f4e7d2c4e3bf7befc05c63d00ed2794c06","tid":1631879,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:37:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ff8994258701d974ff8f80ef8753cee0201bb1a6","tid":1631879,"uid":138409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:39:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mfvpy2S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmfvpy2S.jpg&h=24e88aed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"69383c8196fac4a7dab6d560eadedb1cb065ff23","tid":1631879,"uid":105995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:41:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f76c2cc03192338b91bb9f990e0eaa1dbfc9ec85","tid":1631879,"uid":322775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:41:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d011589a312c040306d19fe05fe6b47f5a7e582e","tid":1631879,"uid":262043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:42:04.000Z","msg":"警察暴力三個月黎越級升就龜縮<br />\n示威者頂唔順, 升級少少暴力就即割<br />\n大家明點解我地咁難做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb8e792b9c091e6616325943b8515836ee96442c","tid":1631879,"uid":119864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:42:37.000Z","msg":"推一推，尋求平衡"},{"pid":"2a0891badf287407860ed9c45e3159386c9d24f9","tid":1631879,"uid":184581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:42:55.000Z","msg":"呢加連登風向係<br />\n<br />\n唔洗外國支持<br />\n外國咩都冇做過<br />\n呢加革命緊<br />\n靠自己啦香港人<br />\n<br />\n唔洗外國支持?<br />\n你地覺得呢加既示威係比邊個睇<br />\n比香港政府? 比中國政府?<br />\n比外國政府去過人櫂法呀"},{"pid":"a890d4ab60586cdff5b746006597db9167c4940b","tid":1631879,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:43:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"2c62c340806ce06243d4f0a3be63407dee9c5bb6","tid":1631879,"uid":74935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:45:57.000Z","msg":"記住黑紅藍黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b8f13b1a0063f1152914f4b09df4a60455cfaec","tid":1631879,"uid":133728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:46:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jYtuLaR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjYtuLaR.jpg&h=f5ef1ebb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"80bc00fa894cd0d9a9d3e0f69d8ece0ad4b870a9","tid":1631879,"uid":263618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a0891badf287407860ed9c45e3159386c9d24f9","tid":1631879,"uid":184581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:42:55.000Z","msg":"呢加連登風向係<br />\n<br />\n唔洗外國支持<br />\n外國咩都冇做過<br />\n呢加革命緊<br />\n靠自己啦香港人<br />\n<br />\n唔洗外國支持?<br />\n你地覺得呢加既示威係比邊個睇<br />\n比香港政府? 比中國政府?<br />\n比外國政府去過人櫂法呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:48:25.000Z","msg":"仲有叫你做民意L!"},{"pid":"4ffa99c7f093a613f2b9a19521213276eee83fb7","tid":1631879,"uid":129340,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:17:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1632038/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1632038/page/1</a><br />\n我諗「暴走的赫胥黎」一撚定好鐘意睇香港01，但係又唔想係連登提香港01，所以先出此下策，真係辛苦曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總結，香港01好熟悉我地既政見、諗法同打字風格，又擅長兩極分化，絕對好有可能就係想搞散連登既重要力量<br />\n你話冇人操縱緊連登言論，人唔笑ＰＯＰＯ都吠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5dfd2db37bbc12a9f784039b88722fb6f6a4263","tid":1631879,"uid":61534,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:24:38.000Z","msg":"我諗「暴走的赫胥黎」一撚定好鐘意睇香港01，但係又唔想係連登提香港01，所以先出此下策，